113
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,550
Absolutely not.

114
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,830
She mustn't choose the nearby courtyard.

115
00:05:37,230 --> 00:05:38,160
I didn't expect

116
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:41,320
