120
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,320
Miss Luo.

121
00:05:50,110 --> 00:05:51,040
Lu Yun?

122
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,350
Why are you here?

123
00:05:55,270 --> 00:05:56,110
Guess.

124
00:05:57,790 --> 00:05:58,720
(Guess again?)

125
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:01,390
