215
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:09,750
Butterfly.

216
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,230
Catching butterflies.

217
00:10:17,470 --> 00:10:18,350
Miss Lingxi.

218
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,400
I must say,

219
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:23,470
