I want...

227
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,840
Wait a moment.

228
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,800
Miss Luo.

229
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:54,840
Lu Yun.

230
00:10:57,910 --> 00:10:58,750
