- It's fine.
- Let me help.

248
00:11:29,877 --> 00:11:31,230
- Rain check.
- Just a quick wipe.

249
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,350
There's plenty of time.

250
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,507
- No rush.
- It's alright.

251
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,860
- Finish it today.
- Gotta go.

252
00:11:34,875 --> 00:11:36,425
- We're not done yet.
- Thank you

253
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,535
