263
00:12:05,110 --> 00:12:07,440
willing to give up time with me,

264
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:08,790
just to remind me,

265
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:12,000
so I won't lose face before others.

266
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:16,910
