599
00:32:36,520 --> 00:32:38,070
I'll catch you.

600
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:42,760
Come here.

601
00:32:43,520 --> 00:32:44,680
Here's my chance.

602
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:46,800
