Want to see more?

645
00:36:09,670 --> 00:36:10,520
No.

646
00:36:12,190 --> 00:36:14,040
Sorry for interrupting.

647
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:16,440
Bye.

648
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,280
So shy and innocent.

649
00:36:19,950 --> 00:36:21,230
Why is she still pretending?

650
00:36:27,630 --> 00:36:30,950
