Astragalus, placenta, and cordyceps.

690
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:35,630
The previous page is fabric, this is herbs.

691
00:38:36,007 --> 00:38:37,315
These are all the usual stuff

692
00:38:37,390 --> 00:38:40,190
