693
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:42,950
Lu Yun?

694
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:45,640
Miss Luo?

695
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:48,560
Sir, Miss Luo's here.

696
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:50,680
Please come in.

697
