708
00:39:26,870 --> 00:39:29,710
I'm sorry about last night.

709
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,560
So, I brought you

710
00:39:32,560 --> 00:39:34,230
a handmade item

711
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:35,640
to apologize.

712
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:39,190
